    },
    {
      "name": "TYPE",
      "description": "Menu type",
      "help": "Menu type (TYPE)\n\nSpecifies the type of menu to be created.\n\nNote: *DSPF must be specified for values to be specified for the Display file (DSPF) and Message file (MSGF) parameters. The Program (PGM) parameter is valid only if *PGM is specified here.\n\nThis is a required parameter.",
      "inputType": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper",
        "restricted": true
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "*DSPF",
          "value": "*DSPF"
        },
        {
          "label": "*PGM",
          "value": "*PGM"
        },
        {
          "label": "*UIM",
          "value": "*UIM"
        }
      ],
      "positional": 2,
      "valueMap": {
        "*DSPF": "F",
        "*PGM": "P",
        "*UIM": "U"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "DSPF",
      "description": "Display file",
      "help": "Display file (DSPF)\n\nSpecifies the display file to be used in creating the menu object. The display file must include one record format with the same name as the display file itself, called the menu format. Help formats may also be included in the file.\n\nHelp formats follow the naming convention #Hxxyy, where xx is the first and yy is the last menu option to which the help format applies. For example, #H0306 would apply to menu options 3 to 6. #H0000 designates the general help for the menu.\n\nThe display file must have a separate indicator area (INDARA keyword) and contain no subfile descriptions.\n\nThis parameter can be specified only if *DSPF is specified for the Menu type (TYPE) parameter.\n\nQualifier 1: Display file\n\nQualifier 2: Library",
      "inputType": "group",
      "required": false,
      "groupKind": "qualified",
      "children": [
        {
          "name": "DSPF_LIB",
          "description": "Library",
          "help": "指定できる特殊値: *LIBL, *CURLIB",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false,
          "defaultValue": "*LIBL",
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "DSPF",
          "description": "Display file",
          "help": "指定できる特殊値: *MENU",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false,
          "defaultValue": "*MENU",
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          }
        }
      ],
      "promptControl": [
        {
